count": 40}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "张智霖曾代言的平台涉诈骗近 12 亿，本人到警局协助调查，经纪公司称去年已终止合作，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "红星新闻消息，9 月 21 日，据媒体报道，香港无牌虚拟资产交易平台 JPEX 涉诈骗案继续发酵，曾为该平台代言的明星张智霖也到湾仔警署协助调查。 21 日晚，张智霖所属经纪公司发布一则「严正声明」回应此事。 声明中称，去年 3 月张智霖曾为该公司拍摄广告片及平面硬照广告，在得知该公司「被证监会列入‘无牌公司及可疑网站名单’」后，已于去年 9 月终止合作。 曾代言平台涉诈骗案！张智霖方严正声明：已于去年 9 月终止合作香港加密平台 JPEX 爆雷，无牌经营，下架交易，上千人报案，涉款近 12 亿港元，哪些信息值得关注？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-a0aa1c9ff392a9254ecc0d38cf1418e8_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "138 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/623247543"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IqLH4177i5JhtEAMaCTEwMDc3ODg4MCDixrOoBjAAOE9AB3IJNjIzMjQ3NTQzeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "8_1695355761.917704", "card_id": "Q_622715700", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 32}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么中国完全拥有长江流域，埃及却没有完全拥有尼罗河流域？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-6ccc918dfb5cd336bdd126579118906f_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "121 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/622715700"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8IqLH4177i5JhtEAMaCTEwMDY2MDYyNyDz96OoBjAAOEpACHIJNjIyNzE1NzAweACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1695355761.920426", "card_id": "Q_622733644", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 15}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价 2023 华为杯研究生数学建模竞赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"te